These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, techno, punk, blues
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, prince, oliveros, tiparillo
1. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the fan of punk##1
2. the fan of country is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
3. the fan of blues is in an odd position##4
4. the oliveros-smoker is on the left or right of the tiparillo-smoker##3
5. the fan of country is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | country | techno | blues | punk |
| Cigar        | montecristo | prince   | tiparillo | oliveros    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, balloon-flower, dahlia, azalea
City: venice, rome, prague, london
1. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
2. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
3. the person traveling to prague is in an odd position##4
4. the person traveling to venice is the person who growszinnia##1
5. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
6. the person traveling to venice is the person who growszinnia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Flower   | dahlia | zinnia  | balloon-flower  | azalea |
| City   | london    | venice | prague | rome    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, gospel, dubstep, folk
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, ship, bike, scooter
1. the fan of folk is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
2. the fan of dubstep is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3
4. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
5. the person driving the tram is in an odd position##4
6. the fan of gospel is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Music-Genre          | folk | dubstep | gospel    | house      |
| Transport   | bike        | scooter     | tram | ship |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, thriller, family, documentary
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, milk, water, 7up
1. the person watching thriller movies is between the person drinking lemonade and the person drinking 7up##2
2. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
3. the person drinking water is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
5. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre         | documentary | crime | thriller | family |
| Beverage   | water       | lemonade   | milk    | 7up  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, hamster, cat, dog
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, documentary, zombie, musical
1. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
2. the person watching documentary movies is the owner of the dog##1
3. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
4. the owner of the hamster is on the far left##1
5. the owner of the cat is in an odd position##4
6. the person watching thriller movies is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Pet   | hamster  | guinea-pig    | cat   | dog       |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | musical | zombie | documentary |

