3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an odd position##4
4. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
5. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Hobby   | sudoku      | singing | hiking | card-games |
| City   | venice | prague     | rome  | nizza  |

