.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, zinnia, balloon-flower, sunflower
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, water, mirinda, hot-chocolate
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who growstulip##1
5. the person who growssunflower is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
6. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Flower   | tulip | sunflower | balloon-flower | zinnia    |
| Beverage     | hot-chocolate | mirinda  | soy-milk     | water |

