.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, mauve, chestnut, brown
There 4 different types of food: cherry, cabbage, apple, raspberry
1. the person eating raspberry is on the left or right of the person who likes mauve##3
2. the person who likes brown is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating raspberry is on the left or right of the person who likes brown##3
4. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
5. the person who likes blood-red is between the person who likes brown and the person who likes mauve##2
6. the person eating cabbage is in an odd position##4
7. the person eating cabbage is between the person who likes blood-red and the person eating apple##2
8. the person who likes blood-red is on the left or right of the person who likes mauve##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Color   | mauve | blood-red      | brown | chestnut |
| Food   | cherry  | raspberry | cabbage    | apple            |

