.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, electrician, dressmaker, freelancer
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, coffee, sprite, mirinda
1. the dressmaker is on the left or right of the photographer##3
2. the photographer is on the right of the electrician##1
3. the person drinking juice is between the person drinking coffee and the dressmaker##2
4. the person drinking juice is in an odd position##4
5. the dressmaker is the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Job   | freelancer | electrician   | photographer | dressmaker |
| Beverage    | mirinda     | coffee | juice     | sprite  |

