.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, aquamarine, light-blue, lilac
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, baccarat, vegafina, blend
1. the person who likes chestnut is the blend-smoker##1
2. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
3. the blend-smoker is between the fonseca-smoker and the person who likes light-blue##2
4. the person who likes chestnut is in an odd position##4
5. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the fonseca-smoker##3
6. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left or right of the baccarat-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Color      | aquamarine       | light-blue   | chestnut | lilac |
| Cigar   | vegafina | baccarat | blend        | fonseca    |

