3. the nigerian is on the left of the french##1
4. the french is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
5. the old-henry-smoker is on the left or right of the blend-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Cigar   | vegafina   | bluemaster   | old-henry      | blend      |
| Nationality      | spanish | nigerian | french | american |

