The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, ice-hockey, skiing, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the person who's sport is skiing is in an even position##4
3. the person who growssunflower is in an even position##4
4. the person who growsiris is on the far right##1
5. the person who growsrose is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person who's sport is skiing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Flower          | tulip | sunflower  | rose  | iris |
| Sport   | skateboarding  | skiing | golf | ice-hockey   |

