.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-14::.
4 different games are played: whist, monopoly, billiard, snooker
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, rugby, volleyball, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is in an odd position##4
2. the person playing whist is in an odd position##4
3. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
5. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
6. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4       |
| Game   | billiard | snooker | whist | monopoly |
| Sport           | skateboarding     | sailing     | volleyball   | rugby         |

