.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, prince, game, fonseca
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, whist, billiard, poker
1. the chaman-smoker is between the person playing mah-jongg and the prince-smoker##2
2. the game-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
3. the prince-smoker is on the left of the person playing poker##1
4. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
5. the person playing poker is in an odd position##4
6. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Cigar   | fonseca | prince         | chaman   | game |
| Game   | billiard    | whist | poker | mah-jongg   |

