.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
House: victorian, wooden, cottage, palace
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, snake, horse, frog
1. the owner of the frog is the cottage house##1
2. the owner of the horse is the victorian house##1
3. the owner of the snake is the palace house##1
4. the cottage house is on the left or right of the palace house##3
5. the victorian house is in an even position##4
6. the cottage house is on the right of the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| House   | wooden | victorian | cottage    | palace |
| Pet   | hedgehog   | horse  | frog | snake     |

