2. the cottage house is in an even position##4
3. the person watching family movies is the cottage house##1
4. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person watching family movies##3
5. the person watching family movies is between the person watching satire movies and the person watching drama movies##2
6. the tower house is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| House         | craftsman   | cottage | palace | tower    |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | family  | satire     | time-travel |

