.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, iced-tea, hot-chocolate, tea
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, soccer, cricket, rugby
1. the person drinking iced-tea is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
3. the person who's sport is soccer is between the person drinking water and the person who's sport is biathlon##2
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
6. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Beverage         | water | hot-chocolate   | tea | iced-tea |
| Sport   | rugby          | soccer | biathlon         | cricket  |

 